"title": "5952: sorrow",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5952",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The human reponse to painful and distressing life situations, especially those involving loss.</p>\n<h2>Sorrow caused by the trials of life</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps90:10\">PSA 90:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps13:1-Ps13:2\">PSA 13:1–13:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps31:9\">PSA 31:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl1:18\">ECC 1:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl2:23\">ECC 2:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer20:18\">JER 20:18</a></p>\n<h2>Sorrow caused by fulfilling God's will</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:6\">1PE 1:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:38\">MAT 26:38</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:27\">PHP 2:27</a></p>\n<h2>Sorrow caused by illness</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa38:2-Isa38:3\">ISA 38:2–38:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps6:1-Ps6:7\">PSA 6:1–6:7</a></p>\n<h2>Sorrow caused by childlessness</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam1:16\">1SA 1:16</a></strong></p>\n<h2>Sorrow caused by parting</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts20:37\">ACT 20:37</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt17:23\">MAT 17:23</a> <em>the disciples' reaction to Jesus Christ predicting his death</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke22:45\">LUK 22:45</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John16:6\">JHN 16:6</a></p>\n<h2>Sorrow caused by bereavement</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen23:2\">GEN 23:2</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John20:11\">JHN 20:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen50:1\">GEN 50:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut34:8\">DEU 34:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam19:2\">2SA 19:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke7:12-Luke7:14\">LUK 7:12–7:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke8:52\">LUK 8:52</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John11:33-John11:35\">JHN 11:33–11:35</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts8:2\">ACT 8:2</a></p>\n<h2>Sorrow caused by national calamities</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps137:1\">PSA 137:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa15:3\">ISA 15:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa22:4\">ISA 22:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer22:10\">JER 22:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer48:17\">JER 48:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek21:6\">EZK 21:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek27:30\">EZK 27:30</a></p>\n<h2>God and sorrow</h2>\n<h3>God is close to those who grieve</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps34:18\">PSA 34:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps10:14\">PSA 10:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa53:4\">ISA 53:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John11:35\">JHN 11:35</a></p>\n<h3>God comforts the sorrowing</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer31:13\">JER 31:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa35:10\">ISA 35:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam3:32-Lam3:33\">LAM 3:32–3:33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John16:20\">JHN 16:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess4:13-1Thess4:14\">1TH 4:13–4:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev21:4\">REV 21:4</a></p>\n<h2>Sorrow in response to human sin</h2>\n<h3>The result of sinning</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps16:4\">PSA 16:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam2:33\">1SA 2:33</a></p>\n<h3>Grief over the failure of others</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor2:4-2Cor2:5\">2CO 2:4–2:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen34:7\">GEN 34:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam20:34\">1SA 20:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra10:6\">EZR 10:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek9:4\">EZK 9:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom9:2\">ROM 9:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor5:2\">1CO 5:2</a></p>\n<h3>Grief over one's own shortcomings</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:4\">MAT 5:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:75\">MAT 26:75</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor7:9-2Cor7:11\">2CO 7:9–7:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas4:9\">JAS 4:9</a></p>\n<h2>Sorrow in response to God's judgment on human sin</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam1:5\">LAM 1:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh1:4\">NEH 1:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer8:21\">JER 8:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer10:19\">JER 10:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer13:17\">JER 13:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer14:2\">JER 14:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek21:6\">EZK 21:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek21:12\">EZK 21:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos5:16-Amos5:17\">AMO 5:16–5:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos8:10\">AMO 8:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic1:8\">MIC 1:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zeph1:15\">ZEP 1:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech12:10\">ZEC 12:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt8:12\">MAT 8:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:30\">MAT 24:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev1:7\">REV 1:7</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ's sorrow in response to human sin</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke19:41-Luke19:42\">LUK 19:41–19:42</a></strong></p>\n<h2>The promise of final deliverance from sorrow</h2>\n<p><em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa35:10\">ISA 35:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev21:4\">REV 21:4</a></p>",
